      "text": "Yes! and yes I can imagine a world without PowerShell.\n\nCause I lived in that world before PowerShell came along.\n\nGUIs were almost all we got on Windows, and cross platform scripting was a distant dream.  There was no object pipeline.  No Get-Command.  No Get-Help.\n\nDark times."
